description.text: Welcome to this charming and beautifully updated traditional-style home located in the desirable Mar Vista neighborhood of Los Angeles for Lease. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is move-in ready and boasts a bright and open floor plan, perfect for modern living. As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that flows seamlessly into the dining area and updated kitchen, featuring stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and ample storage space. The kitchen also includes a large island with seating for casual dining or entertaining and a large family room in the rear. The bedrooms are generously sized and offer plenty of natural light, while the bathrooms have been tastefully updated with modern fixtures and marble finishes. Other features of this home include a cozy electric fireplace, updated floors throughout, and a separate laundry room. Outside, you'll find a beautiful hardscape backyard with plenty of space for outdoor dining and entertaining. The large garage has been converted into a bonus room ADU , perfect for a home office or gym complete with full bath, bedroom and kitchen. Other updates include new roof, full electrical update and panel, plumbing updates, brand new HVAC, tankless water heater, new windows and skylights through out and many more! Located on a quiet tree-lined street, this home is just minutes from local shops, restaurants, and entertainment, with easy access to the 405 and 10 freeways.

The neighborhood offers office space to some of the biggest tech companies and attracts a mix of young professionals who seek to experience the Silicon Valley way of living. Nowadays, an increasing number of locals looking for an urban lifestyle, decide to relocate to Playa Vista and enjoy the shopping and dining. Runaway is the newest shopping area including a food market, movie theater and numerous retail outlets, an ideal destination for the weekends. With Playa Vista's Daily Shuttle you can also get easily around the community. Other things to note Building amenities may have an extra cost. This Blueground apartment has flexible lease options, allowing you to book it for one month, a year, or more. Pets are welcome, though weight limits and breed restrictions apply and may incur fees.
